ygData.messageBody:
http://gameznet.com/eq/

This site has pretty good update for artifact and equipments.

If u read thru the recent updates, all the weaps found are only for tankers
or hybrids, nothing for casters, sigh.

I wonder if it's becoz no one find it or EQ doesnt design much for casters?
Look at Bladestorm, a superb dam 2H warrior only sword, with lvl 49
spells, who need mana anyway? ;( KNN chop here chop there keep casting lvl
49 spells non-stop, sure can win casters, sigh.

Ziltus
(whining for the lack of caster artifacts in EQ)
